<inglise> Council Regulation (EC) No 1456/2001 of 16 July 2001 amending Regulation (EC) No 2549/2000 establishing additional technical measures for the recovery of the stock of cod in the Irish Sea (ICES Division VIIa) </inglise>
<eesti> N&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;rus (E&Uuml;) nr 1456/2001, millega muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 2549/2000, millega kehtestatakse Iiri mere (ICES VIIa rajooni) tursavarude taastamise t&auml;iendavad tehnilised meetmed 16. juuli 2001 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COUNCIL OF THE EUROPEAN UNION, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA LIIDU N&Otilde;UKOGU, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, and in particular Article 37 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, eriti selle artiklit 37, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the proposal from the Commission(1), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse komisjoni ettepanekut, (1) </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the opinion of the European Parliament(2), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Parlamendi arvamust, (2) </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the opinion of the Economic and Social Committee(3), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse majandus- ja sotsiaalkomitee arvamust (3) </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas: </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> (1) The conditions laid down in Regulation (EC) No 2549/2000(4) are intended to ensure that the selectivity of fishing gears deployed in the Irish sea are such that few young cod are captured. </inglise>
<eesti> 1) m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 2549/2000 (4) kehtestatud tingimuste eesm&auml;rk on tagada, et Iiri meres kasutataks ainult selliseid p&uuml;&uuml;givahendeid, millega p&uuml;&uuml;taks v&auml;he noort turska; </eesti>
<inglise> (2) Article 2(1) and (2) stipulate that it is prohibited to use any demersal towed net other than beam trawls incorporating a cod/end and/or extension piece made entirely or partly of multiple twine netting materials and any demersal towed net other than beam trawls incorporating a cod-end and/or extension piece of which the thickness of the twine exceeds 6 mm. </inglise>
<eesti> 2) artikli 2 l&otilde;igete 1 ja 2 kohaselt on keelatud kasutada mis tahes veetavaid p&otilde;hjav&otilde;rke peale piimtraalide, millel on t&auml;ielikult v&otilde;i osaliselt mitmekordsest niidist v&otilde;rgumaterjalist valmistatud noodap&auml;ra ja/v&otilde;i v&otilde;rgupikendus, ning mis tahes veetavaid p&otilde;hjav&otilde;rke peale noodap&auml;ra ja/v&otilde;i v&otilde;rgupikendusega piimtraalide niidi j&auml;medusega &uuml;le 6 mm; </eesti>
<inglise> (3) However, recent scientific advice concurs with the opinion of fishermen that a cod-end and/or extension piece constructed of double twine of thickness no more than 4 mm is technically equivalent to a cod-end and/or extension piece as currently defined. </inglise>
<eesti> 3) uusimad teadusn&otilde;uanded &uuml;htivad kalurite arvamusega, et kahekordsest, kuni 4 mm j&auml;medusest niidist valmistatud noodap&auml;ra ja/v&otilde;i v&otilde;rgupikendus on tehniliselt v&otilde;rdv&auml;&auml;rne praegu kasutada lubatud noodap&auml;ra ja/v&otilde;i v&otilde;rgupikendusega; </eesti>
<inglise> (4) There is a requirement on the part of some fishermen to deploy double-twine cod-ends. </inglise>
<eesti> 4) seep&auml;rast v&otilde;ivad m&otilde;ned kalurid kasutada kahekordsest niidist valmistatud noodap&auml;rasid; </eesti>
<inglise> (5) Article 3 of the current regulation refers to conditions which were relevant only during 2000 and it should therefore be replaced with provisions which set out the required amendment. </inglise>
<eesti> 5) k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artiklis 3 on viidatud ainult 2000. aastal kehtinud tingimustele, mist&otilde;ttu tuleb see asendada vajalike muutmiss&auml;tetega; </eesti>
<inglise> (6) Regulation (EC) No 2549/2000 should accordingly be amended, </inglise>
<eesti> 6) sellest tulenevalt tuleb muuta m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 2549/2000, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 of Regulation (EC) No 2549/2000 shall be replaced by the following: "Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 2549/2000 artikkel 3 asendatakse j&auml;rgmisega: "Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> Notwithstanding the conditions laid down in Article 2(1) and (2), when fishing with towed gears in the Irish Sea, it shall be permitted to use a cod-end and/or extension piece constructed of double-twine netting material of which the thickness of any individual twine does not exceed 4 mm." </inglise>
<eesti> Hoolimata artikli 2 l&otilde;igetega 1 ja 2 kehtestatud tingimustest v&otilde;ib Iiri merel kalastada veetavate p&uuml;&uuml;nistega, mille noodap&auml;ra ja/v&otilde;i v&otilde;rgupikendus on valmistatud kahekordsest, kuni 4 mm j&auml;medusest niidist v&otilde;rgumaterjalist." </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the day following that of its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub j&auml;rgmisel p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
